These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, pear
2 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg
1. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is not the person eating pear##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pear   | nectarine  |
| Sport   | snooker | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, country
2 different pets are kept: goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the goat is not the fan country##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | electronic | country      |
| Pet    | goat  | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, vegafina
