1. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is not the bolivar-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | vegafina  | bolivar    |
| Sport   | handball | sailing |

