.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, march
1. the accountant is in an odd position##4
2. the accountant is not the person who's birthday is in march##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | accountant | social-worker |
| Pet   | december       | march       |

